---
layout: base.njk
title: Texte
description: Gedanken, Gedichte und Impulse von Doris R. Mumenthaler
---
<style>
  .texte-hero { text-align: center; padding: 3.5rem var(--gutter) 2rem; }
  .texte-hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); color: var(--color-ember); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .texte-hero p { color: var(--color-mid); font-style: italic; opacity: 0.8; }
  .texte-ornament { text-align: center; color: var(--color-warm); opacity: 0.4; letter-spacing: 0.5em; margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .texte-list { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--gutter) 4rem; list-style: none; }
  .texte-item { border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,150,127,0.15); }
  .texte-item a { display: block; padding: 1.8rem 0; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
  .texte-item a:hover { opacity: 0.75; }
  .texte-item-type { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-fire); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .texte-item-title { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-style: italic; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-ember); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .texte-item-date { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--color-mid); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .texte-item-excerpt { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-mid); line-height: 1.7; opacity: 0.8; }
</style>

<div class="texte-hero">
  <h1>Texte</h1>
  <p>Gedanken, Gedichte und Impulse</p>
</div>
<div class="texte-ornament">✦ ✦ ✦</div>

<ul class="texte-list">
  {% for item in collections.texte %}
  <li class="texte-item">
    <a href="{{ item.url }}">
      <div class="texte-item-type">{{ item.data.type }}</div>
      <div class="texte-item-title">{{ item.data.title }}</div>
      <div class="texte-item-date">{{ item.date | readableDate }}</div>
      {% if item.data.excerpt %}
      <div class="texte-item-excerpt">{{ item.data.excerpt }}</div>
      {% endif %}
    </a>
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
